{"tid":578782,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"根據歷記載merci 朱古力係秦國人帶入德國","createTime":"2018-03-03T03:21:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-03T13:25:50.000Z","uid":11081,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"00b8445df8ff658f666a044ff5b5bb058c6aaf86","tid":578782,"uid":11081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T03:21:04.000Z","msg":"相傳係有個要去秦國嘅男子為報答一對老人家夫婦借宿，而送左身上唯一一條嘅merci朱古力比佢地作為報答"},{"pid":"ecab05a6cff8a1447ac85fba2dad7511d0bf4016","tid":578782,"uid":11081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T04:23:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0bfa52ff11ae0b4f9a38b183bdcb91214837779","tid":578782,"uid":79298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T04:46:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7301efddc5bf06add45c70f2b12736947d68809e","tid":578782,"uid":40757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T06:09:56.000Z","msg":"個去泰國既男子係咪姓項<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"737c2d0fe07e11c847c8928d6e27ee6139d34e22","tid":578782,"uid":130079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T07:56:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個去泰國既男子係咪姓項<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">唔係 佢姓邱 全名邱傑朗 目前被控運毒 據己知消息佢仲係泰國旅遊中 居住當地一所監獄</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n三名香港青年於泰國曼谷捲入一宗跨國衝關運毒案件，7日內經過迂迴路線橫跨全球五地，終於曼谷機場入境時被關員搜出其行李藏有價值千萬港元的可卡因，隨即被還押當地，面臨最高50年監禁。其中兩女早前認罪被判囚25年，餘下24歲男被告邱傑朗堅拒認罪。"},{"pid":"a27ea04d77b8d327d4a6396df46177f1a01c1de2","tid":578782,"uid":52904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T08:00:57.000Z","msg":"Merci~~~要送我無言的感激"},{"pid":"5620b11f6e8e4db06d6059a7e0838f4604de6c58","tid":578782,"uid":2333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a27ea0